The paper describes an Open Source Software project focused on robotics algorithms, specifically autonomous navigation. This falls under the category of Robotics (cs.RO). Additionally, the project uses Python programming language, which is commonly used in Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Computer Vision (cs.CV) research. The project also includes animations to understand the behavior of the simulation, which could fall under the category of Systems and Control (cs.SY) or Machine Learning (cs.LG).
